

----generating service-----

1.run "ant generate.service" in the base directory
2.copy the "OrderProcessingService.aar" file from build directory to the CARBON_HOME/samples/axis2Server/repository/services directory
3.Start the sample axis2 server



----securing service-------
1.start the ESB
2.copy the content in resources/SecureOrderProxy.xml file to the configuration file of ESB (Source view)




-----running secure client -----
run "ant run.secureClient" in the base directory of the project  